5. feladat

R_1 = 10000;
C = 100 * 10^-9;
R_3 = 2200;
R_4 = 10000;
gamma = R_3 / R_4;
T = 4 * gamma * R_1 * C
T = 8.8000e-04
f = 1/T
f = 1.1364e+03

Mérés
